    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This problem is not present anymore with [`transformItems`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/refinement-list/js/#widget-param-transformitems), introduced in [2.10.0](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/develop/CHANGELOG.md#2100-2018-08-08). This function is applied after `sortBy`.\r\n\r\nYou can read more on how to migrate to this API in [our InstantSearch.js v3 migration guide](https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/upgrade-guides/js/#transformdata-is-replaced-by-transformitems).",
